title: Brazilian Jiu Jitsu Eddie Bravo - The Twister (dvd-rip)
description:
Eddie Bravo Takes us on a tour around his house and a tour around
his grapplig carreer. From his first ever tournament as a bluebelt
to his Abu Dhabi tournament where he submitted Royler Gracie.

Even do i personally think Eddie is a showboater, he stopped competing after he submitted a Gracie and that was really his only accoplishment. After he submitted Royler he practically pronounced himself as one of the greates grapplers of his time witch actually couldnt be more inaccurate.
